WEBVTT

00:01.800 --> 00:03.600
If those things hadn't happened

00:05.880 --> 00:06.880
Have you ever thought

00:08.520 --> 00:09.520
How to live in the future?

00:11.160 --> 00:13.600
Perhaps I could be a female official

00:14.560 --> 00:15.640
For military, there can be Zu Yue

00:16.120 --> 00:16.720
For civil

00:17.120 --> 00:18.760
It might not be impossible for me, Chen Wan'er

00:19.920 --> 00:21.640
Your words are a bit dangerous

00:23.120 --> 00:25.640
If I only wanted to lose myself in nature

00:26.040 --> 00:28.600
Your Majesty would be even more suspicious of me

00:30.280 --> 00:32.480
I truly do want to lose myself in nature

00:33.680 --> 00:36.680
Drink wine, sing songs, race crickets

00:37.720 --> 00:39.680
Be Great Xuan's first carefree prince
